    div.project
      div.project-info
        h1 UpdateImpact
        p UpdateImpact is a tool that allows you visualize, analyze and monitor dependencies tree of your project. The function of the website was to tell potential users about this tool and if / how it can be helpful for them as well as collect some feedback.
        p 
          b My role: 
          | website design and development (HTML/CSS). I also created and developed a series of SVG animations to better illustrate some of the functions of the tool.
        p 
          b Tools: 
          | Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator, HTML, CSS, SVG, CSS animations, iTerm, Sublime Text, node.js, Jade, Stylus.
        p
          a(href="http://www.updateimpact.com/") updateimpact.com 
    div.project
