        h1 Goosta.me
        p Goosta.me is a prototype of a dating website with the feature of video text-chat. It was created for the Static Showdown Hackathon 2015 and won the second place. 
        p 
          b My role: 
          | visual design and direction of the web app, web app development as well as copywriting.
        p 
          b Tools: 
          | Adobe Photoshop, HTML, CSS, CSS animations, iTerm, Sublime Text, Jade, Stylus.
