        h1 Scala Times
        p Scala time is a weekly newsletter about Scala-related news and events. The project consists of newsletter design, website with newsletters archive and stickers design. The main idea behind was to somehow replicate look&rsquo;n&rsquo;feel of classic newspaper.
        p 
          b My role: 
          | design direction, visual design and development of Mailchimp template and website. 
        p 
         b Tools: 
         | Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator, HTML, CSS, Mailchimp Template Engine, Mailchimp API, iTerm, Sublime Text.
        p
          a(href="http://www.scalatimes.com/") scalatimes.com 
    div.project
