        h1 Scalar
        p  Scalar is a one-day one-track Scala conference in Poland. The conference was founded in 2013.
        p 
          b My role: 
          | is everything imaginable:) It started with creation of the logo and visual identity for the conference. I also designed and developed conference website and newsletters template. I designed multiple printing materials for the conference: roll-ups, stickers, leaflets, banners, name tags, etc.
        p 
          b Tools: 
          | Adobe Photoshop, Adobe Illustrator,  Adobe InDesign, HTML, CSS, Mailchimp Template Engine, iTerm, Sublime Text, Jade, Stylus, Grunt.
        p
          a(href="http://www.scalar-conf.com/") scalar-conf.com 
    div.project
