        p  Codebrag is an open-source tool for code-reviewing. The main idea of the product is to simplify the process of code review, make it less tense and more fun and positive. It was in development for 2 years (2013-2015) and I was the only designer on the project. I worked closely with UX designer as well as developers.
        p 
          b My role: 
